| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0913 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3cd715bf-98fb-585c-a83a-de103ed8391b"
